      <title>Apple 即将与 OpenAI 达成协议，在 iPhone 上安装 ChatGPT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/apple-closes-in-on-deal-with-openai-to-put-chatgpt-on-iphone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司已接近与 OpenAI 达成协议，在 iPhone 上使用这家初创公司的技术，这是将人工智能功能引入其设备的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/apple-closes-in-on-deal-with-openai-to-put-chatgpt-on-iphone</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 01:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技巨头开始将东南亚视为下一件大事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/tech-giants-start-to-treat-southeast-asia-like-next-big-thing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚长期以来被视为科技腹地，但如今正迅速成为该行业的重心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-11/tech-giants-start-to-treat-southeast-asia-like-next-big-thing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果称没有主要应用程序开发商接受新的外部支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/apple-says-no-major-app-developers-accept-new-outside-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据向联邦法官提交的证词，目前还没有主要应用程序开发商签约使用苹果公司今年早些时候为其应用程序商店推出的外部支付选项，因为他们支付的费用至少与以前一样高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/apple-says-no-major-app-developers-accept-new-outside-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 23:29:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果在涉及解雇零售员工的劳工诉讼中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/apple-scores-win-in-labor-case-involving-fired-retail-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家劳工关系委员会驳回了对苹果公司在涉及解雇零售店员工的备受瞩目的案件中最严重的指控，但官员们仍然坚称该公司虐待工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/apple-scores-win-in-labor-case-involving-fired-retail-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 22:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 首席运营官表示，现在看到人工智能对经济的全面影响还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-10/openai-coo-says-it-s-too-soon-to-see-ai-s-full-impact-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生成式人工智能的兴起可能尚未从根本上重塑经济，但人工智能领导者预计更大的变化即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-10/openai-coo-says-it-s-too-soon-to-see-ai-s-full-impact-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 20:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
